cs.NI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG

This paper deals with the deployment of unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs) for wireless network applications, which involves aspects of networking (cs.NI), robotics (cs.RO), and control systems (cs.SY). The proposed algorithms also involve machine learning techniques (cs.AI) and optimization (cs.LG).
